This paper discusses the annotation guidelines for Universal Dependencies (UD) in Japanese and the definition of syntactic words in Japanese. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and computational complexity (cs.CY).
